[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1049","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1049.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1333","title":"Red Hat Linux ncftp FTP客户端自动下载选项远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.0 及之前版本中 ncftp 2.4.2 FTP 客户端的自动下载选项存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过在待下载文件名中嵌入 shell 元字符（如 ;、|、` 等），诱使目标用户连接恶意 FTP 服务器并触发自动下载功能，导致任意命令以用户权限执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 ncftp 客户端，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1333"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 ncftp 至 3.0.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复自动下载时文件名中 shell 元字符的过滤问题。如无法升级，可在 ncftp 配置中禁用自动下载选项（auto-download），或避免使用 ncftp -a 自动下载模式，手动确认每个文件后再保存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=89042322924057&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7240.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6111","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#ncftp"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1049.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1048","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1048.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1332","title":"GNU gzexe临时文件漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.0及更早版本中gzip软件包的gzexe程序存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地用户可利用临时文件覆盖其他用户文件，导致文件完整性受损。","severity":"LOW","score":2.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1332"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级gzip软件包至修复版本，或使用mktemp等安全方式创建临时文件；Debian用户可参考DSA-308安装安全更新，Red Hat用户应安装对应补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:50:57.730499565+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88603844115233&w=2","http://www.debian.org/security/2003/dsa-308","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7241.php","http://www.osvdb.org/3812","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#gzip","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/7845"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1048.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1048.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1046","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1330","title":"Sleepycat db库 snprintf 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"db库（版本1.85.4）中的snprintf函数忽略了size参数，导致在使用该函数时无法正确限制缓冲区大小。攻击者可利用此漏洞触发缓冲区溢出，造成信息泄露、权限提升或拒绝服务等危害。攻击者需要本地访问权限，且攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1330"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级db库至1.85.4之后的版本，或应用Red Hat提供的RH42 errata补丁。对于使用db库的应用程序，应避免使用存在缺陷的snprintf实现，改用正确检查size参数的snprintf实现。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:35:31.598835092+00:00","references":["http://lists.openresources.com/Debian/debian-bugs-closed/msg00581.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602661419259&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7244.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#db"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1046.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1328","title":"Red Hat Linux linuxconf 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 系统中 linuxconf 工具在 1.11.r11-rh3 之前版本存在安全漏洞，本地用户可通过符号链接攻击（symlink attack）覆盖任意系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1328"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级 linuxconf 至 1.11.r11-rh3 或更高版本，该版本修复了符号链接竞争条件问题。Red Hat 官方已发布 RH51 安全公告提供更新包，建议用户通过 Red Hat 官方渠道获取并安装补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:21:58.102130741+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90383955231511&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7232.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6068","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh51-errata-general.html#linuxconf"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1033","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1033.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1294","title":"Microsoft Windows 3.51 Office Shortcut Bar 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows 3.51 系统中 Office 快捷工具栏（OSB）启用了备份和恢复权限，这些权限会被从快捷栏启动的文件管理器等程序继承，导致本地用户能够读取其本无权访问的文件夹。攻击者仅需以本地用户身份从 OSB 启动程序即可触发，影响系统文件夹的机密性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1294"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 或更高版本，该问题已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可修改注册表将 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Office\\ShortcutBar 中 BackupRestore 键值设为 0，或通过组策略限制本地用户从快捷栏启动文件管理器以阻断权限继承路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q146/6/04.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/562"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1033.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0980","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0980.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1148","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 FTP 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 及更早版本中的 FTP 服务存在资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过同时发起大量被动模式（PASV）连接请求，消耗服务器连接资源池，导致 FTP 服务无法响应正常用户请求，形成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 Option Pack 等预装 IIS 4.0 的系统，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1148"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-006 提供的补丁程序，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本操作系统（自带 IIS 5.0 及以上版本），以彻底修复该漏洞。对于仍运行 Windows NT 4.0 的系统，建议尽快迁移至受支持的操作系统版本并限制 FTP 匿名访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q189/2/62.ASP","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-006","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1215"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0980.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0006","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0154","title":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 附加点号源码泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 存在源代码泄露漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 ASP 页面 URL 末尾附加一个点号（.），即可绕过服务器脚本执行机制，直接读取 ASP 文件的原始源代码，导致数据库连接字符串、业务逻辑等敏感信息暴露。该漏洞影响 IIS 2.0 及 3.0 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需发送特制 HTTP 请求即可触发，利用难度极低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0154"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"立即升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本（可通过 Windows NT 4.0 Option Pack 安装），该漏洞已在 IIS 4.0 及之后版本中修复。对于已停止支持的旧系统，应迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并部署最新安全更新，同时在 IIS 中禁用不必要的脚本映射作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0154","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20481","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0154.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0154","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0154.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0154.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80405/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0006.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0006.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0002","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 实现拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BSD 衍生系统（包括 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等）的 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证漏洞（CWE-20），未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统崩溃或挂起，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"立即将 FreeBSD 升级至 2.2.8 及以上版本，或将 OpenBSD 升级至 2.3 及以上版本；对于无法升级的系统，下载并安装对应厂商发布的 ip_input.c 补丁。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL，丢弃入站 IP 分片包（若业务不需要分片功能），或部署支持 IP 分片校验的入侵防御系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0001","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0001","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD TCP/IP 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 及 OpenBSD 等 BSD 衍生系统 TCP/IP 协议栈实现中的 ip_input.c 文件存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20），远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标系统内核崩溃或死锁，进而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD、OpenBSD 等多个 BSD 衍生操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。建议升级至修复版本或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0001"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:13.977","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.8 或 3.0 及以上版本，OpenBSD 升级至 2.4 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可在边界防火墙上过滤畸形 IP 分片包，或禁用不必要的 raw socket 处理功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata23.html#tcpfix","http://www.osvdb.org/5707","https://github.com/MarcusGutierrez/complex-vulnerabilities"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0200","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0477","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 远程文件上传与执行漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0 的 Expression Evaluator 组件中 openfile.cfm 文件未对远程用户的文件操作进行有效权限限制，导致存在访问控制缺陷。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞向服务器上传任意文件，进而实现文件显示、删除或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 ColdFusion Server 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0477"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.877","remediation":"升级到 Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.0.1 或更高版本，或移除/限制对 openfile.cfm 的匿名访问权限，通过 Web 服务器配置（如 IIS 或 Apache）禁止外部直接访问该文件。如无法升级，可在应用层实现对 openfile.cfm 的 IP 白名单访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0200.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0455","title":"Allaire ColdFusion Expression Evaluator 远程文件读取删除漏洞","description":"ColdFusion 的 Expression Evaluator 示例应用（exprcalc.cfm）存在未授权访问漏洞，由于未对服务器资源访问进行适当限制，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问该示例页面读取或删除服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Adobe ColdFusion 服务器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0455"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.050","remediation":"删除或移除 ColdFusion 服务器上的 `exprcalc.cfm` 及整个 `/cfdocs/` 示例应用目录；升级到 Adobe 官方仍在维护的 ColdFusion (2021/2023) 最新版本；在 Web 服务器层（IIS/Apache/Nginx）通过访问控制规则禁止外部访问 `/CFIDE/` 和 `/cfdocs/` 目录，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/115"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0892","title":"Netscape Communicator 动态字体处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.7 之前版本在处理动态字体时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可构造一个长度字段值小于字体实际尺寸的恶意字体文件，诱使用户通过受影响浏览器访问包含该字体的网页，触发缓冲区溢出，可能导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Netscape Communicator 浏览器系列，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0892"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.440","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.7 或更高版本，该版本修复了动态字体解析中的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无法升级，可在浏览器设置中禁用动态字体渲染功能，并考虑迁移至仍在维护的替代浏览器以减少风险暴露。通过防火墙阻断外部字体服务器连接也可作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0892"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0949","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1109","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 8.10.0 ETRN命令处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.10.0 之前版本中存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 SMTP 服务器发送大量 ETRN 命令后立即断开连接来触发该漏洞。当攻击者断开连接后，Sendmail 进程仍会继续处理已接收的 ETRN 命令，持续消耗服务器资源，导致邮件服务响应缓慢甚至崩溃，影响正常邮件收发功能。该漏洞利用简单，无需认证，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1109"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.347","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.10.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ETRN 命令处理中连接断开后继续处理导致资源耗尽的问题。如无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制 ETRN 命令来源 IP，或通过防火墙限制 SMTP 端口入站连接频次作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94632241202626&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780566911948&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7760.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/904","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19701","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1109","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr/GHSA-jw39-vxm9-j3xr.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/sendmail_etrn_dos.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000955.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1109.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0949.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0919","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0919.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1066","title":"id Software Quake 1 服务器 UDP 反射放大漏洞","description":"id Software Quake 1 服务器在处理 UDP 游戏连接初始请求时存在流量放大缺陷。攻击者可伪造源 IP 地址向目标 Quake 1 服务器发送特制的初始连接请求包，服务器会向该伪造的源地址（即受害者）返回大量响应流量，从而导致反射型放大攻击。此漏洞与 Smurf 攻击类似，允许远程攻击者利用第三方 Quake 1 服务器作为放大器对目标主机实施分布式拒绝服务攻击（DDoS），攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，影响所有使用 id Software Quake 1 服务器软件的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1066"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Quake 1 官方最新补丁或改用现代分支服务端（如 ezQuake、QuakeSpasm 等），这些版本已修复 UDP 流量放大问题。在网络层面启用 uRPF（单播反向路径转发）过滤源地址欺骗包，并在防火墙限制目标 UDP 端口 26000-27000 的入站速率，防止被用于放大攻击。如不再需要对外提供游戏服务，建议直接在防火墙层面禁用该端口的公网映射。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94589559631535&w=2","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1066"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0919.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1682","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0997","title":"WU-FTPD FTP Conversion 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 2.4.2至2.6.2版本中启用了FTP文件转换功能时存在命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过上传包含特殊畸形文件名的文件，该文件名在传输过程中被作为参数传递给转换程序（如tar或uncompress），从而导致任意命令在服务器端执行。该漏洞影响多版本WU-FTPD服务器，CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高危。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需具备FTP上传权限即可触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0997"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.343","remediation":"升级至 wu-ftpd 2.6.3 或更高版本以修复此漏洞；若无法升级，在 ftpaccess 配置文件中关闭 conversion 功能，注释或移除相关 conversion 规则，并限制匿名用户上传目录不可执行转换操作。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 tar、uncompress 等转换程序的 setuid 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/2003/dsa-377","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20563","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0997","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0997.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/wu_ftpd_site_exec.nasl","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/debian_DSA-377.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml"}]